WEBVTT

00:14.009 --> 00:19.278
There are so many of you who have got realization very recently.

00:19.303 --> 00:22.882
Some people are such who have got their realization a few days back

00:22.907 --> 00:26.576
and there are some who have got their realization long back

00:26.783 --> 00:29.207
those who have understood

00:29.232 --> 00:34.117
what is one's own consciousness and how does it work?

00:34.142 --> 00:36.050
How does it work?

00:36.075 --> 00:40.375
And how do we go on adopting it.

00:40.955 --> 00:44.197
Because of being three types of people here

00:44.222 --> 00:46.646
I will have to repeat some of the points and tell you

00:46.671 --> 00:51.577
so that you will be able to understand, what does realzation mean

00:52.202 --> 00:54.792
What are the qualities of a realized person?

00:54.817 --> 00:56.927
Last time also I have told you a lot about

00:56.952 --> 00:59.066
what are the qualities of a realized person?

00:59.543 --> 01:06.100
And next, how should we be in our realized state

01:07.549 --> 01:10.044
In this way I will tell you about these three categories.

01:13.601 --> 01:15.324
This at least should be done

01:15.349 --> 01:17.047
that whatever you have studied currently

01:17.072 --> 01:19.834
whatever you have read here as well, forget that this moment.

01:27.020 --> 01:32.621
First of all, the question is what is the meaning of realization?

01:32.955 --> 01:36.061
When you come to My feet

01:38.465 --> 01:43.910
many people are told that they haven't got their realization

01:43.935 --> 01:47.853
and many are told that they have got their realization.

01:47.878 --> 01:54.358
It means first of all that realization has no connection with

01:54.398 --> 02:01.633
your outward body, mind or intellect but with some inner being

02:01.658 --> 02:05.618
which in some people gets connected, whereas in others doesn't.

02:08.909 --> 02:14.599
During your realization, when you are at My feet, at that time

02:14.624 --> 02:17.198
those who feel on the hands

02:17.223 --> 02:21.735
they feel the flow coming with a greater force on their hands.

02:22.338 --> 02:28.579
And you also feel something going into your feet.

02:30.294 --> 02:35.832
All around yourself, man's environment's

02:35.857 --> 02:39.885
and all around the whole world

02:39.910 --> 02:41.016
the CHAITANYA SHAKTI ( power of consciousness)

02:41.041 --> 02:44.686
is playing, inside and outside.

02:45.210 --> 02:48.284
For example, every tree has power of consciousness inside it.

02:48.309 --> 02:50.396
Its leaves also have the power of consciousness.

02:50.421 --> 02:52.574
Its root also has.

02:52.599 --> 02:53.967
In the same way

02:53.992 --> 02:59.384
the power of consciousness resides even in the whole universe.

02:59.670 --> 03:01.967
Just as Ether is present all around

03:01.992 --> 03:05.441
in the same way, this CHAITANYA SHAKTI is moving all around

03:05.466 --> 03:09.235
and inside, outside, everywhere is its abode.

03:13.358 --> 03:14.513
And the same shakti (CHAITANYA)

03:14.538 --> 03:19.820
goes on doing whatever complete work of JAD SHAKTI is to be done.

03:20.480 --> 03:27.542
Now this power within us is known as kundalini.

03:27.709 --> 03:32.649
But Kundalini is a word

03:32.674 --> 03:34.507
although, God has not

03:34.532 --> 03:38.378
given any meaning of anything, nor has He given any word

03:38.403 --> 03:39.680
For example, (God) has not named  anything

03:39.705 --> 03:43.561
but human beings have named it Kundalini.

03:43.862 --> 03:55.202
The power called Kundalini inside our being

03:55.227 --> 04:00.072
is situated at the base of our spine in the triangular bone.

04:00.097 --> 04:05.410
I am about to release an article about that in Manohar Shakti.

04:05.435 --> 04:08.065
You better read all the details of that

04:08.090 --> 04:12.256
and you will come to know the scietific names of that too.

04:12.281 --> 04:14.291
Many of you know that

04:15.827 --> 04:18.886
your attention

04:27.012 --> 04:35.692
your attention when you are an ordinary human being

04:38.811 --> 04:41.482
is on your body, intellect and mind, all the three.

04:41.507 --> 04:46.406
You go on seeking that thing which gives you joy.

04:48.628 --> 04:54.882
When you are at one with that CHAITANYA SHAKTI

04:58.522 --> 05:01.876
because of kundalini awakening

05:01.901 --> 05:06.347
at Sahastrara, your attention gets one with that

05:06.372 --> 05:13.416
then your attention goes to your Kundalini.

05:13.441 --> 05:16.228
And the moment it goes to your own kundalini

05:16.426 --> 05:20.317
your attention goes to other's kundalini as well.

05:21.729 --> 05:25.199
That means, till now your attention could go to three places

05:26.312 --> 05:28.818
and now it goes to fourth place

05:28.843 --> 05:31.126
which is NIRAKAR SHAKTI ( formless power).

05:31.151 --> 05:35.872
And the moment you go into that state, you go beyond your thoughts

05:35.897 --> 05:39.992
and watch you mind, intellect and body in the witness state.

05:42.299 --> 05:49.901
Now those from whose hands the cool breeze is flowing

05:53.634 --> 05:59.214
these vibrations we have got so effortlessly

05:59.239 --> 06:02.535
that we don't know what a great thing we have got!

06:02.560 --> 06:07.684
The first biggest problem is

06:07.709 --> 06:10.898
'How did we get such a great thing so easily?'

06:11.422 --> 06:13.924
For example, just understand like this

06:13.949 --> 06:19.213
that a human birth we get so easily

06:19.238 --> 06:24.026
that we don't know that to get a human birth

06:24.051 --> 06:27.067
after struggling for so many births

06:27.092 --> 06:30.034
with great difficulty we get human birth

06:30.725 --> 06:32.726
and its rebirth

06:33.284 --> 06:36.344
after a great struggle for all the births we had

06:36.403 --> 06:38.703
and after a lot of seeking, one can get rebirth.

06:39.347 --> 06:41.925
But this is happening so easily

06:41.950 --> 06:45.490
that we are not able to understand its value.

06:46.191 --> 06:50.048
We also think that how did it happen so quickly.

06:52.155 --> 06:56.633
The reason was that until now you were seeking everything outside

06:56.658 --> 06:59.021
and it is within you.

06:59.109 --> 07:01.730
For example, there is a diamond within you

07:01.755 --> 07:04.064
and you are searching for it all over the world

07:04.089 --> 07:05.948
and it was found lying within you only.

07:06.000 --> 07:08.647
Then someone tells you that the diamond is here only

07:08.672 --> 07:10.151
and tells you even the route.

07:10.176 --> 07:11.296
You pick up the diamond.

07:11.321 --> 07:14.642
Will you say,"How did i get it in no time?"

07:14.667 --> 07:15.758
You will only say

07:15.783 --> 07:19.057
"I was here only and why i was searching for it all over the world?"

07:19.658 --> 07:23.403
This is actually happening.

07:23.428 --> 07:26.699
When we get such a state on account of Sahaj Yoga

07:26.724 --> 07:33.790
actually we get it so easily

07:33.815 --> 07:36.396
that we cannot understand how did we achieve this state?

07:38.217 --> 07:45.543
Or say, that in the modern age, as you suddenly reach Moon

07:46.829 --> 07:47.865
You may not even know

07:47.890 --> 07:49.683
if you could reach Moon in a moment.

07:49.708 --> 07:52.859
If such an arrangement could be made

07:52.884 --> 07:58.307
it is quite possible that you will feel

07:58.332 --> 08:03.498
where did we reach?

08:03.523 --> 08:04.731
How is it possible?

08:04.756 --> 08:08.111
How did we reach Moon in a moment?

08:08.136 --> 08:12.016
In the same way this incident

08:12.112 --> 08:15.917
takes place so easily

08:16.619 --> 08:19.014
this incident takes place so easily

08:19.039 --> 08:22.172
that it is quite natural for you to feel so.

08:22.197 --> 08:26.146
But, if something happens easily

08:26.436 --> 08:29.506
or with a great difficulty

08:29.531 --> 08:32.784
you remember one which takes place with a great difficulty.

08:32.809 --> 08:35.841
And one can understand that, which happens with difficulty.

08:35.866 --> 08:37.997
It is man's nature.

08:38.022 --> 08:41.134
And a man considers himself blessed in that

08:41.159 --> 08:44.007
which he gets by doing his duty.

08:44.032 --> 08:47.035
Even if his father gives him one lakh rupees

08:47.060 --> 08:49.195
he doesn't understand its importance.

08:49.220 --> 08:52.556
If he earns even two rupees by dint of his hard work

08:52.581 --> 08:53.582
he has great importance for it

08:53.607 --> 08:55.238
as he feels it is because of his own effort.

08:55.245 --> 08:57.554
It is an indication of his own ego.

08:57.579 --> 09:00.025
It is the nature of his Ego.

09:00.050 --> 09:03.488
But in Sahaj Yoga when there is no Ego

09:03.513 --> 09:06.512
there is no question of getting anything because of Ego.

09:06.769 --> 09:09.927
So ego being dissatisfied

09:09.952 --> 09:12.433
raises such doubts within

09:12.458 --> 09:15.155
that why it is so in Sahaj?

09:16.818 --> 09:20.314
Methods of your own realization

09:20.339 --> 09:21.511
and all that happens

09:21.536 --> 09:23.473
(NOT CLEAR)

09:23.498 --> 09:25.914
many of you have felt it.

09:25.939 --> 09:29.775
you will find a new method in each book

09:29.800 --> 09:31.718
that when self realization takes place

09:31.743 --> 09:34.184
it happens like this, like that.

09:34.280 --> 09:37.697
Now how many of them are realized and how many are not, God knows.

09:39.259 --> 09:41.029
Out of you, those who have got realization

09:41.054 --> 09:43.922
and have acquired your ascent slowly

09:43.947 --> 09:46.754
you know that when a person gets realization

09:46.779 --> 09:48.750
only his Sahatrara breaks

09:48.775 --> 09:52.506
and he gets one with the vibrartions.

09:53.943 --> 09:58.770
After that he remains still here only

09:58.795 --> 10:02.654
and his attention goes to his own and other's kundalini

10:02.679 --> 10:05.850
but the vibrations that are coming inside his own self

10:05.875 --> 10:07.402
sometimes stop suddenly.

10:07.427 --> 10:10.151
And if he puts his hand on his head, he will find

10:10.176 --> 10:14.538
that the spot which had become soft, has become hard again

10:14.578 --> 10:15.578
gets calcified.

10:18.637 --> 10:20.934
(NOT CLEAR)

10:20.959 --> 10:25.315
You have got realization just yesterday and it has calcified.

10:25.340 --> 10:27.345
What is the reason?

10:27.370 --> 10:28.583
The reason is that

10:28.608 --> 10:34.421
our ego and superego inside us are definitely removed

10:34.446 --> 10:37.025
our attention comes in the center definitely

10:37.050 --> 10:40.789
but it grows again and and become one.

10:46.108 --> 10:48.909
It grows again becomes one

10:51.557 --> 10:54.657
and when it grows and becomes one

10:54.682 --> 10:58.277
the calcification takes place again and the flow stops

10:58.302 --> 11:00.793
but even then you can feel kundalini.

11:01.564 --> 11:02.743
But how?

11:02.768 --> 11:06.212
If after that you meditate and put your hands towards ME

11:06.562 --> 11:11.253
you will feel that this hand or thumb has caught up.

11:11.446 --> 11:12.802
They have got realization

11:13.065 --> 11:15.391
because those who are not realized

11:15.416 --> 11:18.421
those who are not realized, if they put their hands towards ME

11:18.468 --> 11:20.745
they won't feel anything.

11:20.770 --> 11:22.628
But those who have got their realization

11:22.653 --> 11:27.245
they will say ,"Mataji my this finger has caught up."

11:29.731 --> 11:32.889
They will feel that this finger of mine has caught up.

11:33.031 --> 11:35.329
or this finger of mine has caught up

11:35.354 --> 11:36.078
i am not getting in this

11:36.103 --> 11:36.894
i am getting in this (Pointing to particular fingers).

11:37.533 --> 11:40.724
Out of those who will be knowledgeable, they will understand

11:40.749 --> 11:44.217
which finger points to which chakra

11:44.744 --> 11:46.737
It is not an imaginary situation.

11:46.762 --> 11:49.188
This cannot be known through mental calculations.

11:49.213 --> 11:50.415
I didn't tell you.

11:50.440 --> 11:51.946
Because had I told you so

11:51.971 --> 11:54.078
people would have said, " Mataji is just talking uselessly."

11:54.103 --> 11:56.345
I said,"you find out."

11:56.370 --> 11:58.322
And when he put his hands like this

11:58.347 --> 12:00.534
and his this finger started burning

12:00.576 --> 12:03.339
I said, (To some sahaj yogi) put your hand on his Nabhi Chakra

12:03.364 --> 12:04.957
Nabhi Chakra was working.

12:04.982 --> 12:06.767
Close your eyes and feel within

12:06.792 --> 12:08.461
which chakra of yours is working?

12:08.486 --> 12:09.590
Nabhi Chakra is working

12:09.615 --> 12:11.312
and when you put your hand towards him

12:11.337 --> 12:12.848
which finger is burning, this finger is burning.

12:13.007 --> 12:15.988
It means that this finger corresponds to his Nabhi Chakra

12:16.304 --> 12:23.155
and everybody's this finger will catch.

12:23.180 --> 12:25.138
So without any discussion the point is that

12:25.163 --> 12:27.019
you may write a book or whatever you like to write

12:27.044 --> 12:31.464
the way a thing happens, it happens like that only.

12:31.489 --> 12:33.285
Yesterday, regarding Gyaneshwar ji

12:33.310 --> 12:35.790
a gentleman was arguing too much with me.

12:35.815 --> 12:37.110
Had Gyaneshwar ji been alive today

12:37.135 --> 12:39.453
I would have talked to Him Myself.

12:39.478 --> 12:41.469
He was also searching the method

12:41.494 --> 12:43.548
how to make this to understand

12:43.573 --> 12:47.980
but it was not possible as he died at a very young age.

12:48.005 --> 12:50.152
Like this, because of many such untimely deaths

12:50.177 --> 12:53.195
a lot of misconceptions have spread in the world.

12:53.220 --> 12:56.005
And he wrote a book, this was his another mistake.

12:56.030 --> 12:58.024
Because of that, I am scared of writing a book

12:58.049 --> 13:00.611
as just on writing a book, people will start learning it by heart

13:00.636 --> 13:03.419
and that too may condition people.

13:06.970 --> 13:09.963
And in this what happens and what does not happen

13:09.988 --> 13:11.769
exactly you must think

13:11.794 --> 13:15.535
that every minute i have a new experience, it is a new thing.

13:15.560 --> 13:17.932
We are new people, everything is new.

13:17.957 --> 13:20.860
We have to know everything new, we will settle down as new (people).

13:20.885 --> 13:22.637
Like a small child from his childhood

13:22.662 --> 13:25.044
listens a single word and goes on learning it

13:25.251 --> 13:27.572
checks repeatedly and understands it.

13:27.597 --> 13:30.449
In the same way those who are new

13:30.474 --> 13:34.465
those who have come in this kingdom of God

13:34.490 --> 13:37.509
should understand the divinity of this kingdom.

13:37.534 --> 13:39.886
His vision should be different.

13:39.911 --> 13:42.485
It has a great speciality that it has been named DIVYALOK.

13:42.510 --> 13:45.195
I would pass by here and would feel joyous to read its name

13:45.220 --> 13:47.420
Some great thoughtful person has named it.

13:47.445 --> 13:50.003
How beautiful the name is DIVYALOK?

13:51.629 --> 13:54.542
I didn't know that God will make all the arrangements here itself.

13:54.567 --> 13:58.111
Wish the other kindness be bestowed on us.

13:58.136 --> 14:01.410
It is a very beautiful place.

14:01.435 --> 14:04.089
The divine kingdom in which you have descended

14:04.114 --> 14:08.096
to know its divinity, you should think

14:08.121 --> 14:10.422
that all this is new.

14:10.447 --> 14:11.737
It is all original.

14:11.762 --> 14:13.814
There is all new experience.

14:13.839 --> 14:17.075
Somewhere written, old, shattered

14:17.100 --> 14:19.627
what others have experienced, it is not that.

14:19.652 --> 14:22.912
It is what we have to experience.

14:25.249 --> 14:31.125
So, absolutely new, like a new child

14:31.150 --> 14:33.690
in the same way, you come to a new form.

14:33.715 --> 14:35.866
The first thing important is that

14:35.891 --> 14:41.063
you pay attention to the newest concepts, all new.

14:41.088 --> 14:45.238
Till date nobody has experienced such a thing anywhere.

14:45.263 --> 14:49.496
This experiment was never successful so speedily, in this world.

14:49.521 --> 14:52.214
Because I too have come to this world many times

14:52.239 --> 14:55.337
and I tried to do this work many times.

14:55.362 --> 14:59.127
This work was successful for the first time in this birth (of Mine).

14:59.152 --> 15:05.369
So, the little incompleteness that has remained in everybody

15:05.394 --> 15:06.968
you have to complete that.

15:06.993 --> 15:10.869
You have come to complete that incompleteness.

15:10.894 --> 15:13.357
You have not come to overpower or reduce anyone

15:13.382 --> 15:20.829
You have come to complete whatever incompleteness has been left out.

15:20.854 --> 15:22.838
Now you think that

15:22.863 --> 15:32.454
you are new people of a new world and new dimension

15:32.479 --> 15:37.017
and you have to give guidance for the whole world.

15:37.042 --> 15:43.501
So, many realized people sitting under one roof

15:43.526 --> 15:47.946
are being blessed by that Divine Power

15:47.971 --> 15:54.200
How much powerful energy flows specially from.

15:54.225 --> 15:57.616
It is not so from other people of the world.

15:57.641 --> 16:01.898
You are aware of it. There is no doubt about it now.

16:01.923 --> 16:03.328
Some people have a little bit doubt.

16:03.353 --> 16:03.940
Its reason is that

16:03.965 --> 16:05.009
they have got their realization a few days back only.

16:05.034 --> 16:12.042
Within a few days they too will feel it.

16:12.067 --> 16:16.342
Then it becomes necessary

16:16.367 --> 16:22.171
that you understand your importance.

16:22.196 --> 16:27.267
Your greatest quality is that now you are in fourth dimension.

16:27.292 --> 16:30.266
which fourth dimension have you got?

16:32.759 --> 16:35.100
which fourth dimension have you got?

16:35.125 --> 16:37.756
The Chaitanya Shakti that is flowing in you

16:37.781 --> 16:40.806
you are standing in that.

16:40.831 --> 16:43.524
Now how can you go from this to that?

16:43.549 --> 16:48.207
it is a great important point, you try to understand it.

16:48.232 --> 16:54.400
Now how you can get off into it, manage to be in that state

16:54.425 --> 16:57.965
is an important point.

16:57.990 --> 17:00.683
Now if you observe your attention

17:00.708 --> 17:03.893
you will observe that there occurs a type of expansion

17:03.918 --> 17:05.723
it also stretches within itself.

17:05.748 --> 17:07.318
Feel your attention

17:07.343 --> 17:09.414
introspect your attention

17:09.439 --> 17:12.665
It seems as if it goes somewhere else

17:12.690 --> 17:13.885
and if you want you can get it back.

17:15.593 --> 17:19.492
Its expansion is going on and if you want you can get it back also.

17:19.517 --> 17:27.189
It is like a baloon which is called in Marathi 'phuga'.

17:27.214 --> 17:30.909
You blow it and it will go like this and then come back.

17:32.293 --> 17:35.131
In the same way you watch your attention

17:35.156 --> 17:40.452
your attention can go towards anything as well as return back

17:40.477 --> 17:44.175
NOT CLEAR

17:44.200 --> 17:47.710
See our attention has gone towards some object.

17:47.734 --> 17:52.258
For example, your attention is on some saree.

17:52.283 --> 17:57.777
Your attention has gone towards saree but you can pull it back.

17:57.802 --> 18:03.337
As per your desire, you can minimize or maximize your attention

18:03.362 --> 18:05.902
and you can take it wherever you want.

18:05.927 --> 18:08.543
But you are fully involved in the center.

18:08.568 --> 18:09.793
For example, take the case of sea.

18:09.818 --> 18:13.944
the water from the sea overflows all its banks and returns back.

18:13.969 --> 18:16.988
but in the center, everything of the sea

18:17.013 --> 18:19.968
has its own abode (VASTAVYA)

18:19.993 --> 18:23.464
all that is VASTAVYA

18:23.489 --> 18:25.647
that which is going to happen, is inside.

18:25.672 --> 18:29.464
Its reaction is awareness.

18:29.489 --> 18:32.518
It goes to something and returns back.

18:32.543 --> 18:36.007
You learn detachment from this.

18:36.032 --> 18:39.217
From this only we tell you to get detatched.

18:39.242 --> 18:41.873
For example that car came here.

18:41.898 --> 18:45.190
It is a minor issue. it is giving out some smell

18:45.215 --> 18:47.777
First of all, it gave out foul smell, o.k!

18:47.802 --> 18:51.059
If you pay attention to the foul smell, we will feel it.

18:51.084 --> 18:52.373
You divert your attention, you will not feel foul smell.

18:55.695 --> 18:58.959
You are getting the power of detachment within you.

18:58.984 --> 19:02.249
By and by you practice over your attention

19:02.274 --> 19:09.975
Man endowed with all religious knowledge is sitting in the center.

19:10.000 --> 19:11.825
He is paying attention to everything.

19:11.850 --> 19:14.471
What is this, what is this, what is this?

19:14.496 --> 19:17.348
This is also,This is also, people say all this is mine.

19:17.373 --> 19:19.146
Pay your attention to that

19:19.171 --> 19:21.697
and the moment you pay attention to that

19:21.722 --> 19:24.324
you know very well that I can take it back as well from there.

19:24.349 --> 19:27.094
Your attention cannot get involved in any such thing

19:30.399 --> 19:36.065
and whatever love you will attatch to it or do anything

19:36.090 --> 19:39.086
that will only hit it with a stone and come back

19:39.111 --> 19:42.877
but will not get attatched to it.

19:42.902 --> 19:44.379
Try to understand it.

19:44.404 --> 19:47.097
Eirlier when you would pay your attention to a thing

19:47.122 --> 19:48.302
with the help of your thoughts.

19:48.327 --> 19:50.742
For example, if anything moves from here

19:50.767 --> 19:54.165
that will go on moving as a whole and its range will be maintained.

19:54.190 --> 19:55.896
NOT CLEAR

19:55.921 --> 19:57.868
Now the one that will get released from here

19:57.893 --> 20:00.076
will take a round turn and then will come towards you.

20:00.101 --> 20:01.445
There is nothing in the center.

20:01.473 --> 20:01.935
It is all vacant.

20:06.220 --> 20:07.901
