35:41.632 --> 35:45.105
You think yourself that there is someone to give you this knowledge

35:45.130 --> 35:46.182
some one to convince you

35:46.207 --> 35:50.097
that after realization, how much dangerous the situation is.

35:50.122 --> 35:53.474
Anyone can catch you , you are absolutely small children

35:53.499 --> 35:59.469
and such small children

36:01.263 --> 36:05.276
it is necessary

36:05.300 --> 36:08.907
to safeguard your state

36:08.931 --> 36:13.799
You are always under MY protection

36:13.824 --> 36:16.363
and everytime I take care of you

36:16.388 --> 36:19.256
and a lot of love for all of you.

36:19.701 --> 36:22.813
Feel proud and also enjoy myself a lot.

36:22.838 --> 36:25.734
That is why I have sons and children.

36:25.759 --> 36:27.947
It is a matter of pride for ME

36:27.972 --> 36:28.976
(NOT CLEAR)

36:29.001 --> 36:33.044
But what you have got, don't waste that on useless things.

36:37.076 --> 36:39.281
All of you have experienced it.

36:39.306 --> 36:41.832
Sometime you ask Yadav, he will tell you.

36:41.857 --> 36:43.970
Just now Mr. Patil came and he was telling ME.

36:44.540 --> 36:46.714
Here are ladies, many of them can relate their experiences.

36:46.739 --> 36:49.530
How did they experience and how did they correct themselves.

36:49.840 --> 36:53.095
If there is any problem, I can definitely solve that

36:53.120 --> 36:54.820
but you also learn to do so a little bit.

36:54.845 --> 36:57.776
You also do, you also learn, you also know.

36:57.801 --> 37:00.661
You are the doctor and you are the medicine.

37:01.877 --> 37:04.741
It is going to flow from you only.

37:04.766 --> 37:06.763
Even if you get injured a little bit, doesn't matter.

37:06.788 --> 37:08.253
Mother is there to set you right.

37:08.278 --> 37:10.768
It is not a matter of worry.

37:10.792 --> 37:13.106
Such people were not existing earlier.

37:13.131 --> 37:15.935
Because even the people who have got their realization

37:15.960 --> 37:18.101
say how did we get realization, God save us.

37:18.800 --> 37:21.090
Such were the people in earlier days.

37:21.115 --> 37:23.642
After getting realization, they would sit with tongs in their hands.

37:23.667 --> 37:27.265
It was not their fault. They would beat them mercilessly.

37:27.290 --> 37:29.251
If somebody would come who would burn them

37:29.276 --> 37:31.415
from whom they would get heat

37:31.440 --> 37:33.177
they would beat him with tongs.

37:33.202 --> 37:35.553
They were called CHIMTEWALLA BABA (an ascetic carrying tongs).

37:35.578 --> 37:37.177
I have seen them in MY childhood

37:37.202 --> 37:40.646
I am so surprised that whosoever comes is hit with tongs.

37:40.671 --> 37:43.090
Whosoever is there call ME with great love.

37:43.115 --> 37:46.015
I have never hit anyone by any tong.

37:46.040 --> 37:47.539
Who will go to them?

37:47.564 --> 37:51.776
Its reason is that there was nobody to explain and make them understand.

37:51.801 --> 37:54.031
Now you are curing so many diseases of people

37:54.056 --> 37:56.460
you have cured even diseases like cancer.

37:56.485 --> 37:58.935
Such type of diseases you have cured just easily.

37:58.960 --> 38:00.698
So many types of negativities you have removed

38:00.723 --> 38:02.061
because you have done such a lot of work.

38:02.086 --> 38:05.368
It is sure that you will catch something or the other

38:05.393 --> 38:08.967
but there is a dispensary for that also.

38:08.992 --> 38:12.248
For you too there is a dispensary and a person who can tell you

38:12.273 --> 38:14.414
and also one who can explain the minutest details.

38:14.439 --> 38:16.518
There is nothing to be afraid of.

38:16.543 --> 38:17.931
Even then, if you are scared

38:17.956 --> 38:22.217
that means you cannot proceed further in this life.

38:22.242 --> 38:24.840
This is about realized people.

38:24.865 --> 38:28.225
But we should understand one more thing.

38:28.250 --> 38:31.356
There are many such saints who have died

38:31.381 --> 38:33.016
but they are not able to take their birth.

38:33.041 --> 38:34.134
Many people are trying

38:34.159 --> 38:35.427
but they are not able to take their birth.

38:35.452 --> 38:37.927
Because they are not getting such a being

38:37.999 --> 38:39.336
or may be there is some other problem.

38:39.361 --> 38:43.161
Such saints are planning like this

38:43.186 --> 38:46.911
that those who can never get realization among us

38:46.936 --> 38:48.788
there are so many in our country (INDIA)

38:48.813 --> 38:49.889
those who will never get realization

38:49.914 --> 38:52.300
because they have their such previous karmas.

38:52.325 --> 38:56.792
Some have done planchette [calling spirits]  where they have got stuck up

38:56.817 --> 38:59.202
or any such thing.

39:00.285 --> 39:02.786
They say that we should come into them.

39:03.757 --> 39:05.917
You will feel some negativity in them

39:05.942 --> 39:07.768
but they are not harmful.

39:07.793 --> 39:09.107
There is no need to quarrel with them.

39:09.132 --> 39:11.341
Although very clerical people among you

39:11.366 --> 39:14.095
will feel it quite strange that how is MATAJI saying such a thing.

39:14.209 --> 39:15.020
Don’t provoke them

39:15.045 --> 39:16.377
because if you provoke them then

39:16.402 --> 39:17.742
it can happen that the bhoots can go into them.

39:17.767 --> 39:19.841
Bhoots are already within them.

39:19.866 --> 39:21.530
If there will be no bhoots then the saints will come.

39:21.555 --> 39:23.681
When the saints come, our work will be done.

39:23.706 --> 39:26.439
That is why in many people the saints have resided.

39:26.464 --> 39:27.698
They have a great desire.

39:27.723 --> 39:31.784
They have expressed it to ME that they want to come.

39:31.809 --> 39:34.479
But if we come in the form of small children

39:34.504 --> 39:36.337
how can they help you?

39:36.690 --> 39:39.224
So it is better that such people who come to you

39:39.249 --> 39:41.551
and those who are unable to get realization

39:41.739 --> 39:42.444
can't see

39:42.468 --> 39:43.846
there are many people like that.

39:43.871 --> 39:45.613
Even if they are not getting realization

39:45.638 --> 39:47.096
there is no need to argue with them.

39:47.121 --> 39:48.407
They will keep on coming always.

39:48.432 --> 39:52.026
They will come for four years, for six years or even for ten years

39:52.051 --> 39:54.305
but don't argue with them.

39:54.330 --> 39:55.943
They are coming, let them sit.

39:55.968 --> 39:58.415
You know they have not got their realization.

39:58.440 --> 40:00.674
A person who has got realization once, will go on getting realization.

40:00.699 --> 40:03.298
But the one who has not got realization and is going in and out

40:03.323 --> 40:04.590
there is no need to get involved with him.

40:04.615 --> 40:07.015
Do you remember (NOT CLEAR)

40:07.040 --> 40:08.939
Only the saints will work on them

40:08.964 --> 40:11.007
because without that the work is not getting accomplished.

40:11.032 --> 40:15.217
All negativities will be removed only by saints

40:15.242 --> 40:17.834
because you cannot see these

40:17.859 --> 40:20.574
and you cannot go to the other world.

40:20.599 --> 40:22.642
So allow them to do this work.

40:22.667 --> 40:25.542
They say that they will come and go on doing the work

40:25.567 --> 40:27.407
and go on spreading MY work.

40:27.432 --> 40:30.229
They will not cure any one of you or do anything

40:30.254 --> 40:32.171
but they will do such type of work

40:32.196 --> 40:34.642
that they are for example such people with others

40:34.667 --> 40:36.947
they will be more strong in language.

40:36.972 --> 40:40.126
They will speak, will drag people ( to Sahajyoga)

40:40.151 --> 40:42.511
and bring many more people who want to come.

40:42.536 --> 40:45.856
There was such a person who had even written an article about ME.

40:45.881 --> 40:49.201
But he was too much scared and he ran away.

40:49.226 --> 40:51.078
They are never going to get realization.

40:51.103 --> 40:52.907
A decision was taken in his name

40:52.932 --> 40:55.003
and he was told to write about ME and he started writing about ME.

40:55.028 --> 40:59.209
After that the poor fellow got involved in some case

40:59.233 --> 41:01.173
that there was a different environment

41:01.198 --> 41:02.595
and he got involved in that.

41:02.620 --> 41:04.709
Such people should be saved.

41:04.734 --> 41:07.888
Keep them with saints. Atleast they will be well behaved

41:07.913 --> 41:09.010
and by coming to Sahajyoga

41:09.035 --> 41:10.782
they will never be attacked by any negativity

41:10.807 --> 41:12.131
they won't have any physical trouble

41:12.156 --> 41:13.348
they won't have any mental trouble

41:13.373 --> 41:14.510
and they will have wisdom

41:14.535 --> 41:16.630
because the saints do not trouble anyone.

41:16.655 --> 41:18.921
That is why saints are within them.

41:18.946 --> 41:20.691
but those who are heads of some religious establishment

41:20.716 --> 41:22.132
they too are hovering over you.

41:22.157 --> 41:23.426
They will help you.

41:23.451 --> 41:25.447
They are also helping you.

41:25.472 --> 41:28.141
They will protect you a lot.

41:28.166 --> 41:31.778
You will have physical, mental and intellectual protection.

41:31.950 --> 41:34.108
He will look after your worldly affairs.

41:34.133 --> 41:36.412
He will pay attention to your household

41:36.437 --> 41:38.941
will take care of your family and household.

41:38.966 --> 41:42.413
But you should completely surrender to God.

41:42.438 --> 41:44.798
There is a great responsibility on you.

41:44.823 --> 41:46.851
Today I wanted that

41:46.818 --> 41:49.925
if anyone has any question or wants to discuss anything

41:49.950 --> 41:50.544
they can do.

41:50.568 --> 41:56.288
Mr. Shroff told ME

41:56.313 --> 42:00.393
and you be like a gardener in a garden

42:00.418 --> 42:04.321
You have to see how to maintain this garden

42:04.346 --> 42:09.111
how to set it, how to plant it, how to maintain it

42:09.136 --> 42:11.052
everything you have to think.

42:11.077 --> 42:13.826
You think about it and tell ME how it can be done.

42:13.851 --> 42:15.939
One thing he said was correct.

42:15.964 --> 42:18.392
He was saying that if we give realization

42:18.417 --> 42:21.742
and don't do the follow ups

42:21.767 --> 42:23.775
then realization gets lost.

42:24.160 --> 42:25.160
It is a fact.

42:27.662 --> 42:31.659
if we even after giving realization

42:31.684 --> 42:35.115
don’t follow up and protect them

42:35.140 --> 42:38.163
we don't take them forward, take care of them

42:38.188 --> 42:41.762
it is quite possible that their realization will be lost

42:41.787 --> 42:43.711
And then it will awaken after a very long time

42:43.736 --> 42:44.944
till then they will be in trouble.

42:44.969 --> 42:46.976
So, all of you have to be collective

42:47.001 --> 42:49.722
and everybody should meet atleast once a month.

42:49.747 --> 42:53.131
Every realized person should meet once every month.

42:53.156 --> 42:58.919
Make it such a way that every month a letter should go to each one.

42:58.991 --> 43:01.992
Or publish a newspaper which everyone reads.

43:02.017 --> 43:04.476
It should be distributed for one month

43:04.501 --> 43:05.889
and no money should be charged.

43:05.914 --> 43:09.449
Do not pay money anywhere nor borrow from anyone.

43:09.474 --> 43:11.421
Do not get involved in money transaction

43:11.446 --> 43:14.052
even for making ashram, the land that Government will give.

43:14.077 --> 43:16.143
Even in that, never think like that

43:16.168 --> 43:17.888
then you will grow vegetables in that

43:17.913 --> 43:19.330
and then you are selling vegetables.

43:19.355 --> 43:22.183
There is no need of doing all this business.

43:22.208 --> 43:23.865
We don't have to earn money.

43:23.890 --> 43:25.070
Today you must have read

43:25.095 --> 43:27.576
What is the condition of the Chairman of State bank?

43:27.601 --> 43:30.144
He went to the ashram, gave him ninety lakhs

43:30.169 --> 43:32.401
20 lakhs were given elsewhere for making furniture.

43:32.425 --> 43:34.908
Is furniture made in ashram?

43:34.933 --> 43:35.607
Use your senses.

43:37.075 --> 43:40.564
You please do not make furniture to sell it

43:40.589 --> 43:42.684
otherwise tomorrow we will see that

43:42.709 --> 43:44.663
these people are making furniture.

43:44.688 --> 43:45.866
There is no need for that.

43:45.891 --> 43:48.406
It is forbidden for you to do gardening there.

43:48.431 --> 43:49.354
For this, you can engage a gardener.

43:49.379 --> 43:51.563
For doing such work ,there are many people.

43:51.588 --> 43:53.058
You are here for a special work.

43:53.083 --> 43:56.620
You have to help in meditation, vibrations

43:56.645 --> 43:59.663
and redressing the problems of others

43:59.688 --> 44:02.915
to give them vibrations, to awaken theiir chakras

44:02.940 --> 44:04.350
and to give them realization

44:04.375 --> 44:06.528
and so far as money is concerned , be away from it.

44:06.553 --> 44:09.072
Do not get involved in money transactions.

44:09.097 --> 44:13.680
Money should be arranged, take so much money

44:13.705 --> 44:15.810
and keep its account, there is no need for it.

44:16.069 --> 44:18.859
If you get involved with money and its accounts

44:18.884 --> 44:20.511
you will get caught up always.

44:20.536 --> 44:24.810
There is absolutely no connection of God and money.

44:24.835 --> 44:27.684
If someone gives you a place for free, it is fine.

44:27.709 --> 44:30.000
If he doesn't give , no problem.

44:30.025 --> 44:31.393
It is all God's work.

44:31.418 --> 44:34.013
If you are sitting at a place, if someone gave you a place to sit

44:34.038 --> 44:36.050
then he was God’s man who gave it

44:36.075 --> 44:38.852
and if he doesn't give, it does not matter.

44:38.877 --> 44:41.954
No one becomes God if he owns a place or land.

44:41.979 --> 44:43.724
There are many ashrams.

44:43.749 --> 44:45.129
You have not to make any ashram.

44:45.154 --> 44:46.931
So, do not pay your attention to that.

44:46.956 --> 44:49.233
Please do not pay your attention towards that.

44:49.307 --> 44:53.739
That we are going to do this or that, or do business in an ashram.

44:53.764 --> 44:55.733
I will never allow this to happen.

44:55.758 --> 44:57.825
And when I see that you are stuck in some business

44:57.850 --> 45:00.362
then it is not MY responsibility.

45:00.387 --> 45:04.077
You don't have to do any business of any type.

45:04.102 --> 45:08.314
You don't have to collect money in any way, for nothing at all.

45:08.339 --> 45:11.628
One person said to me that he will sell MY photos

45:11.653 --> 45:13.877
and then that money he will give money to ashram.

45:13.902 --> 45:17.342
I said, “Which ashram? Whose money you have to give? Who said so?

45:17.825 --> 45:20.362
NOT CLEAR

45:20.387 --> 45:23.302
There is no need to worry about all this.

45:23.327 --> 45:26.348
The One who is doing and looking after us is HE.

45:26.373 --> 45:28.839
We are not doing our work. We are doing His work.

45:28.864 --> 45:32.489
If HE wants, He will give and doesn’t want, won’t give.

45:32.513 --> 45:35.284
And the same work we do night and day of eating ‘filth’

45:35.309 --> 45:38.009
and if we are going to come here and do it, then it is of no use.

45:38.034 --> 45:39.947
Don’t give ME ideas like this.

45:39.972 --> 45:42.552
Because few people have given it and it pains Me badly.

45:42.577 --> 45:45.731
Please do not give such types of suggestions.

45:45.756 --> 45:47.886
That way I am very straight and innocent

45:47.911 --> 45:49.368
but I am very clever as well.

45:49.393 --> 45:51.683
I am not going to be bound by these tricks.

45:51.708 --> 45:53.993
I am telling you beforehand

45:54.018 --> 45:56.453
that if you try to trick Me into money matters

45:56.478 --> 45:57.822
I am not going to support you.

45:57.847 --> 46:00.545
Whether you get realization or not, it does not concern Me.

46:00.570 --> 46:01.934
First of all, you must realize that

46:01.959 --> 46:07.588
there is no connection between money and realization anywhere.

46:07.613 --> 46:10.862
The other thing is that there is no connection of this to politics.

46:10.887 --> 46:13.062
There will be such people also who will come to you

46:13.087 --> 46:14.826
and ask you to stand for election

46:14.851 --> 46:16.668
as you have such a large following.

46:16.693 --> 46:19.598
If you want to go into politics you better go

46:19.623 --> 46:22.041
but politics has been created by humans and not by God.

46:22.066 --> 46:24.743
If you have to stand at a place that belongs to God

46:24.768 --> 46:28.088
it has nothing to do with politics and government.

46:29.819 --> 46:30.953
This is the first thing to understand

46:32.887 --> 46:35.244
and it has no connection with position.

46:35.269 --> 46:37.800
If you think that you are a very senior trustee

46:37.825 --> 46:40.762
here, there are just two to four people

46:40.787 --> 46:45.448
but if someone thinks I am a very senior secretary

46:45.473 --> 46:48.583
or i am a chairman

46:48.607 --> 46:53.444
there is no connection with any ‘chair’.

46:53.469 --> 46:55.679
And neither is there any throne or seat.

46:55.735 --> 46:57.088
Remember this first of all.

46:57.113 --> 46:58.701
It is to talk amongst ourselves.

46:58.726 --> 47:01.505
It has neither any seat nor any throne.

47:01.530 --> 47:05.773
Shree Mataji speaks in Marathi

47:08.912 --> 47:11.606
Marathi

47:11.631 --> 47:13.338
No need to make any special seat.

47:13.363 --> 47:15.662
Who is sitting on Adi Shankaracharya’s seat now?

47:15.687 --> 47:16.882
Someone who is absolutely non-realized

47:16.907 --> 47:18.055
So nothing doing.

47:18.080 --> 47:19.503
Nobody is going to sit on any vehicle.

47:19.528 --> 47:21.400
Everyone is sitting on his own  vehicle.

47:21.425 --> 47:22.995
When you sit on someone’s  vehicle

47:23.020 --> 47:26.761
you are always afraid of being removed from that  vehicle.

47:26.786 --> 47:29.105
Sit on your own vehicle

47:29.130 --> 47:31.485
and by ruling over your own selves from your own vehicle

47:31.510 --> 47:35.325
a lot will be done.

47:35.350 --> 47:39.626
Just tie a knot of these few things.

47:39.651 --> 47:43.896
Third thing

47:43.921 --> 47:49.007
a noble character, good conduct and divinity

47:49.032 --> 47:52.507
without this you cannot proceed at all in this path.

47:52.532 --> 47:54.830
If you have some bad habits

47:54.855 --> 47:57.090
you will have to make an effort to give up.

47:57.115 --> 47:58.257
Take a vow on My feet.

47:58.282 --> 48:02.233
Actually, the fact is that now you have shakti within you.

48:02.258 --> 48:08.531
For example, Indians have a very bad habit of criticizing others.

48:08.556 --> 48:10.319
We are now connected with love

48:10.344 --> 48:11.877
We are all brothers and sisters.

48:11.902 --> 48:14.251
If something has happened amongst each other

48:14.276 --> 48:16.575
can be that someone’s foot slips

48:16.600 --> 48:20.042
it is not necessary that you go and discredit him all over the world.

48:20.067 --> 48:23.856
Come and tell Me, I can set it right.

48:23.881 --> 48:27.304
But to save your brothers even at the cost of your life

48:27.329 --> 48:29.213
it is your full responsibility

48:29.238 --> 48:35.448
for your brothers and sisters.

48:35.473 --> 48:38.468
For that whatever you have to do, we will have to save him.

48:38.493 --> 48:40.055
It is a moral responsibility.

48:40.080 --> 48:42.694
It does not mean you have to pay money for that.

48:42.719 --> 48:45.287
Do not lend any money to anyone.

48:45.312 --> 48:47.664
If someone asks for money don’t give a penny.

48:47.689 --> 48:51.128
There is no need to lend money to anyone.

48:53.210 --> 48:58.185
If some person, in his spiritual life

48:58.217 --> 49:01.660
where his Kundalini is being destroyed or falling

49:01.685 --> 49:04.167
if someone has got into some bad habits

49:04.192 --> 49:07.890
all of you should help with the help of your love.

49:09.208 --> 49:12.224
Till the Purity does not come into us fully

49:12.249 --> 49:15.399
our work will be left incomplete.

49:15.424 --> 49:19.228
You should know this that the eyes of the whole world are on you.

49:19.253 --> 49:23.113
By fixing these decorate Diwali with these.

49:23.138 --> 49:25.984
People's attention is not on the house

49:26.009 --> 49:29.096
but on the lamps that burn.

49:29.121 --> 49:33.213
The attention of whole world is on every one of you

49:33.238 --> 49:35.321
that after all those who have got realization

49:35.346 --> 49:36.513
and are curing sicknesses in the world

49:36.538 --> 49:37.767
how are they leading their own life?

49:42.576 --> 49:44.219
Criticizing this and criticizing that

49:44.244 --> 49:45.912
although till now I have not seen such criticism.

49:46.214 --> 49:48.220
Till today there is no criticism against (Sahaj yoga).

49:48.245 --> 49:49.744
But there is every possibility of it.

49:49.769 --> 49:52.960
If there is any problem, just come and tell me.

49:52.985 --> 49:54.924
No one is perfect as yet.

49:54.949 --> 49:58.615
So if anyone has any problem, just come and tell Me.

49:58.640 --> 50:04.720
I will cure that problem Myself.

50:04.745 --> 50:05.980
And whatever shortcomings you have

50:06.005 --> 50:07.799
never feel shy sharing with anyone (your brothers and sisters0.

50:07.824 --> 50:09.702
All of you are brothers and sisters.

50:09.727 --> 50:12.850
As soon as you say “This is catching in me”, it can be cleared.

50:12.875 --> 50:14.766
If you don’t tell them how can it be cleared?

50:15.436 --> 50:18.931
There is no need to feel bad as you know that every one catches

50:18.956 --> 50:23.782
All are doctors and doctors take free treatment among themselves.

50:23.807 --> 50:26.310
So all of you can get cured free of cost.

50:29.345 --> 50:32.333
You must have brotherhood among yourselves

50:32.358 --> 50:35.901
and keep your attention towards an extremely pure life.

50:38.504 --> 50:40.982
So purity is very necessary.

50:41.007 --> 50:42.992
Without that this work cannot be done.

50:43.017 --> 50:45.669
If I had spoken about purity before

50:45.694 --> 50:47.404
then it would have been a question of perversion

50:47.429 --> 50:50.445
that you clear out on one end and catch on another.

50:50.470 --> 50:52.874
You clear out on the second thing and you catch a third thing.

50:52.899 --> 50:54.897
But after realization, this problem is no more there.

50:54.922 --> 50:56.424
After realization

50:56.449 --> 50:58.129
a hole that has been made here ( on the top of the head)

50:58.154 --> 50:59.856
because of that everything will go out from here (Sahastrara).

50:59.881 --> 51:05.573
You leave one thing and it will go out from here.

51:05.598 --> 51:09.433
It will go out fully. It is not going to enter anywhere else.

51:09.458 --> 51:12.846
That is the advantage of the hole that has been made here

51:12.871 --> 51:14.888
Whatever habits you have, keep these in your mind

51:14.913 --> 51:16.627
and then take out from here.

51:16.652 --> 51:19.155
Wherever the habit is, you will feel heaviness.

51:19.180 --> 51:22.349
On the Nabhi, some like to eat a lot.

51:22.374 --> 51:25.131
It does'n't look nice to overeat. Pay attention to your Nabhi.

51:25.156 --> 51:27.219
Your Nabhi is here, a little higher.

51:27.244 --> 51:31.242
From Nabhi then slowly remove it.

51:31.267 --> 51:36.306
Then everything will come out, all the filth will come out.

51:36.331 --> 51:37.945
The reverse wind is blowing.

51:37.970 --> 51:39.715
Today, it is blowing from the reverse side.

51:39.740 --> 51:44.864
Just now Mr. Jode told me that now he breaths from here (top of head).

51:44.889 --> 51:46.930
It is good!

51:46.955 --> 51:50.465
seeing, listening

51:50.490 --> 51:54.711
smelling, taste everything is from here.

51:54.736 --> 51:56.934
Finally everything happens due to consciousness

51:56.959 --> 51:58.990
and when consciousness has come on the top of the head

51:59.015 --> 52:00.402
then it will be here only.

52:01.636 --> 52:03.309
The beating of the heart

52:03.334 --> 52:06.584
the work of the whole body is done from here (Sahasrara).

52:06.609 --> 52:10.641
So anything that you want to take out from within yourself

52:10.666 --> 52:13.149
then just press it and take it out from here

52:13.174 --> 52:15.826
Your habits will go by itself.

52:15.851 --> 52:18.403
All your habits will be released from here

52:18.428 --> 52:20.225
because now there is a hole, it is very helpful.

52:20.250 --> 52:21.650
The hole was not there

52:21.675 --> 52:24.658
So like they say that if you press the ocean from one side

52:24.683 --> 52:25.852
it grows on the other.

52:25.877 --> 52:30.267
But if a hole is made in it then it will flow out.

52:30.292 --> 52:32.902
So if you press it on the side, it will not go to the other side.

52:32.927 --> 52:34.546
It will come out.

52:34.571 --> 52:38.288
Make an effort and look towards yourself

52:38.313 --> 52:41.098
as to what is impure within us.

52:41.123 --> 52:44.070
Like our Mother’s name is Nirmala, so we too have to be Nirmal (Pure).

52:44.095 --> 52:48.280
And what is impure within us, and not within others.

52:48.305 --> 52:50.482
Again we come to the same thing.

52:50.507 --> 52:53.074
Just now I was watching that some were looking at others.

52:53.099 --> 52:57.427
No, no, I mean what is within us. Which “Hum” [Spirit] is it?

52:57.452 --> 53:01.030
What is it that is within us?

53:01.055 --> 53:04.032
These are our misidentifications

53:04.057 --> 53:06.563
means that we have thought of ourselves as Christians

53:06.588 --> 53:08.708
we are Muslims

53:08.733 --> 53:11.772
we are Hindus and the rest are useless.

53:11.797 --> 53:13.696
This is a misidentification.

53:13.721 --> 53:17.495
We Indians are the best, and the rest are useless.

53:17.519 --> 53:23.419
These all are misidentifications and all are false.

53:23.444 --> 53:28.464
There is just one truth that we are humans.That is the reality.

53:28.489 --> 53:32.391
First thing is that if you know this answer

53:32.416 --> 53:36.467
then you will understand the rest that you are.

53:36.492 --> 53:41.320
One must keep watching all your misidentifications each moment.

53:41.345 --> 53:43.419
What are we thinking at this moment?

53:43.444 --> 53:53.558
We are thinking that I have to go home and make food.

53:53.583 --> 53:57.549
NOT CLEAR

53:57.574 --> 54:02.987
Some are thinking about what happened in the office today?

54:03.012 --> 54:05.173
What will happen in the office tomorrow?

54:05.198 --> 54:07.070
People are thinking about various things

54:07.095 --> 54:09.078
and I know what all they are thinking about.

54:09.103 --> 54:11.607
You should listen to My lecture in Thoughtlessness.

54:11.632 --> 54:15.852
Not with these thoughts.

54:15.877 --> 54:20.025
The One who cooks for us is sitting here. We do not make food.

54:20.363 --> 54:22.701
Think about this once

54:23.672 --> 54:25.707
that when such a miracle has happened

54:25.732 --> 54:28.291
that just sitting here you have gone beyond thoughtlessness.

54:28.575 --> 54:30.229
We will see more miracles.

54:33.875 --> 54:39.788
Because matter is also made from that same Conscious Power.

54:39.813 --> 54:44.594
See this also.The Cook is sitting there.

54:44.619 --> 54:48.530
And your questions will get answered like this.

54:48.555 --> 54:51.182
As soon as you go into thoughtless awareness you will understand

54:51.207 --> 54:53.903
that you have come under the protection of God

54:53.928 --> 55:01.249
and in thoughtless awareness, this help has come inside your being.

55:01.274 --> 55:04.196
If you have any questions please ask Me today

55:04.221 --> 55:08.848
But do not meditate today as a lot of time has gone for meditation

55:08.873 --> 55:12.066
Next time we will have meditation.

55:12.091 --> 55:15.659
And at this moment let us have a puja or recite mantras

55:15.684 --> 55:18.316
by which you will be specially given a protection

55:18.341 --> 55:20.693
by which you will have no problem.

55:20.718 --> 55:22.561
There are many devils roaming around outside

55:22.586 --> 55:24.403
and you can get into trouble.

55:24.428 --> 55:25.559
You must come.

55:25.584 --> 55:27.098
After this, the programme is in Pune.

55:27.123 --> 55:29.278
Those who want to come to Pune can come to Pune also

55:29.303 --> 55:33.979
but if you attend this two week program, it will be better.

55:34.911 --> 55:36.876
Now, what I have said, just think about it.

55:36.901 --> 55:39.272
Now with My lecture, you cannot not get conditioned.

55:39.297 --> 55:42.403
Your conditionings will also go away.

55:42.428 --> 55:44.262
The main point is that it will be over.

55:44.287 --> 55:47.585
Conditionings will go away from here (Sahasrara).

55:47.610 --> 55:50.050
After realization, the greatest benefit is that

55:50.075 --> 55:52.213
nothing will now stick to you.

55:52.238 --> 55:55.645
Its gross will not stick to you, only its consciousness may stick.

55:56.464 --> 56:01.984
Even if I speak in Urdu, Farsi or French

56:02.009 --> 56:08.614
but the CHAITANYA that is flowing through the words will come into you

56:08.639 --> 56:11.537
So with this, the vibrations will flow into you.

56:11.562 --> 56:14.118
There is no need to understand the language.

56:14.143 --> 56:17.852
The love that is flowing from within is what is touching you.

56:17.877 --> 56:19.839
Like you may not know the name of the flower

56:19.864 --> 56:22.126
its honey will go into you.

56:22.151 --> 56:24.042
the fragrance will flow into you.

56:24.067 --> 56:26.759
The fragrance is the Consciousness

56:26.784 --> 56:28.860
and the flower is (NOT CLEAR)

56:28.885 --> 56:30.584
So, even if you don’t understand the name

56:30.609 --> 56:32.328
the fragrance comes to everyone.

56:32.353 --> 56:35.369
Each human being can smell a flower.

56:35.394 --> 56:38.871
Everyone can tell, he may be an English, French or Indian.

56:38.896 --> 56:42.177
Everyone can smell its fragrance.

56:42.202 --> 56:43.854
It doesn't need any language.

56:43.879 --> 56:45.120
In the same way

56:45.145 --> 56:48.841
God’s fragrance which is the Conscious Power can flow into anyone

56:48.866 --> 56:50.040
whatever may be his language.

56:50.065 --> 56:54.299
In this speech what I wanted to say was different

56:54.324 --> 56:57.602
and what I wanted to give was different.

56:57.627 --> 56:59.476
That has got established inside.

56:59.501 --> 57:02.845
Whatever the problems were, will be taken out from here (Sahasrara)

57:02.870 --> 57:04.218
A churning goes on inside

57:04.243 --> 57:05.000
And on account of that

57:05.025 --> 57:06.289
and whatever the chakra after taking a round

57:06.314 --> 57:07.830
wants to get rid of throw that out

57:07.855 --> 57:10.255
take it out with the help of your hand.

57:10.280 --> 57:12.280
Some may get a heavy head, take out that ( heaviness).

57:12.305 --> 57:15.984
If you are catching from someone, don’t worry

57:16.009 --> 57:19.503
even your heaviness will also go out with it.

57:19.528 --> 57:23.663
Like I said yesterday, take out with the left hand.

57:23.688 --> 57:33.008
If anyone wants to ask any question, please ask.
